HEADWORD: Pearlaceous
<hw>Pearl*a"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling pearl
or mother-of-pearl; pearly in quality or appearance.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> iridescent, nacreous, opalescent, opaline,
pearlaceous.</syn>⟦br⟧
